[I] An extended version of tolua, a tool to integrate C/C++ code with Lua

[T] tolua++ is an extended version of tolua, a tool to integrate C/C++ code
[T] with Lua. tolua++ includes new features oriented to c++ such as:
[T] support for std::string as a basic type and support for class templates.

[U] http://www.codenix.com/~tolua/

